  <brief_title>Effects of the Low-level Laser Therapy on Inflammatory Profile of the Patients With Coronary Artery Bypass Surgery</brief_title>
  <official_title>Effects of the Low-level Laser Therapy on Inflammatory Profile on Patients With Coronary Artery Bypass Surgery: A Randomized, Controlled Clinical Trail</official_title>
